. We show that\nthese careful quantitative dissections provide a template for a predictive\nunderstanding of the many more complex regulatory arrangements found across all\ndomains of life.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Dec 2018 23:06:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-01"}
