 AMIGO\nwill have a limited range of observable area. The propulsion system also serves\nas a rough attitude control system (ACS), as it enables pointing and regulation\nover where the lander is positioned via an array of MEMS thrusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Dec 2018 02:03:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-01"}
